title: Женский Квартал
overview: Humorous production project Studio Kvartal 95 - Womens Kvartal of the participants were 14 girls. This show is filled with bright dance and vocal numbers, humorous scenes and witty jokes that will help women to easily look at the current events in life. On the stage of the Women's Quarter will joke about love, marriage, household and family topics, as well as the stars of show business.
